<section class="every-fan">
	<div class="every-fan__inner">
		<h2 class="every-fan__heading">Something for Every Kind of Fan</h2>
		<p class="every-fan__lead">Whether you're here for the match, the music, or the atmosphere, the Los Angeles World Cup 26&trade; Fan Zone at Downtown Burbank was designed as a full-scale entertainment experience for everyone.</p>

		<div class="every-fan__cards">
			<article class="every-fan__card every-fan__card--coral">
				<h3 class="every-fan__card-heading">Soccer Fans</h3>
				<p class="every-fan__card-text">Catch every moment on massive LED screens surrounded by the energy of fellow supporters, live match reactions, and an electric stadium-like atmosphere.</p>
			</article>

			<article class="every-fan__card every-fan__card--purple">
				<h3 class="every-fan__card-heading">Food Lovers</h3>
				<p class="every-fan__card-text">Indulge in the Culinary Experience Package, explore the free international street fair, and discover a wide variety of local restaurants, bars, cocktails, and curated food experiences throughout Downtown Burbank.</p>
			</article>

			<article class="every-fan__card every-fan__card--pink">
				<h3 class="every-fan__card-heading">Music &amp; Nightlife</h3>
				<p class="every-fan__card-text">Enjoy live music, DJs, performances, and post-match celebrations that keep the excitement going long after the final whistle.</p>
			</article>
		</div>

		<p class="every-fan__closing">From global soccer culture and international flavors to live entertainment and community celebration, the event will transform Downtown Burbank into one of Southern California's most dynamic destinations throughout the tournament.</p>

		<a
			href="https://tickets.cbfproductions.com/e/los-angeles-world-cup-26-fan-zone-downtown-burbank/tickets?utm_source=fanzone-dtb&utm_medium=every-fan-cta&utm_campaign=worldcup26"
			target="_blank"
			rel="noopener noreferrer"
			class="every-fan__btn"
		>
			Get Tickets
		</a>
	</div>
</section>

